the technique of Buddhist Palm?

252
00:28:12.335 --> 00:28:13.848
Hey there. young man.

253
00:28:14.241 --> 00:28:15.268
Wait a minute.

254
00:28:15.388 --> 00:28:18.747
Whoa. Amazing! Amazing!

255
00:28:19.832 --> 00:28:23.985
Do you know you have a
very special aura about you?

256
00:28:24.393 --> 00:28:28.225
Oh. you're still a child. but
you have the bone structure

257
00:28:28.250 --> 00:28:31.016
and the chi-flow
of a kung-fu genius.

258
00:28:31.675 --> 00:28:35.482
If your chi-flow can be channeled.
then you will be invincible.

259
00:28:36.579 --> 00:28:39.726
Remember the old saying.
you cannot escape your destiny.

260
00:28:40.352 --> 00:28:45.056
The duty of upholding world peace
and punishing evil will be yours.

261
00:28:45.527 --> 00:28:46.527
Uh-huh!

262
00:28:46.720 --> 00:28:50.607
Here. the Buddhist
Palm manual of training.

263
00:28:50.773 --> 00:28:56.057
It's priceless. But since this is
fate. I can let you have it for $10.

264
00:28:56.647 --> 00:28:58.639
BUDDHIST PALM MANUAL

265
00:29:02.758 --> 00:29:05.147
-You gave him all the money you had?
-Yes.

266
00:29:05.358 --> 00:29:08.589
I had been saving it so I could
become a surgeon or a lawyer one day.

267
00:29:08.794 --> 00:29:11.020
But this seemed like a
chance to save the world.

268
00:29:36.069 --> 00:29:37.398
Let her go!

269
00:29:56.687 --> 00:29:59.314
Oh. do-it-yourself kung-fu!

270
00:29:59.537 --> 00:30:02.143
The whole Buddhist
Palm for 20-cents.

271
00:30:02.530 --> 00:30:04.037
You must be loaded.

272
00:30:04.062 --> 00:30:05.865
Have you killed anyone lately?

273
00:30:17.756 --> 00:30:22.869
The total idiot and the deaf
mute. What a bunch of losers!

274
00:30:23.866 --> 00:30:27.719
I realized then that good guys
never win. I want to be evil.

275
00:30:28.726 --> 00:30:31.010
I want to be a ruthless killer!

276
00:30:32.207 --> 00:30:34.062
-Lets get some ice cream!
-Where?

277
00:30:35.401 --> 00:30:37.355
Wait! Do you have vanilla?

278
00:30:37.458 --> 00:30:38.657
I want chocolate!

279
00:30:50.559 --> 00:30:53.165
What's the matter. have you
never seen an ice cream thief?

280
00:30:57.802 --> 00:30:59.291
Catch us if you can!

281
00:31:14.630 --> 00:31:17.569
If you're such kung-fu masters.
take your show on the road.

282
00:31:17.699 --> 00:31:20.479
You belong in the circus. not
in a respectable neighborhood.

283
00:31:20.766 --> 00:31:22.999
I never want to see
your ugly faces again.

284
00:31:23.530 --> 00:31:24.910
Don't be so hard on them.

285
00:31:25.219 --> 00:31:27.376
I'm sure they had a reason
for doing what they did.

286
00:31:27.993 --> 00:31:29.767
Everyone has his reasons.

287
00:31:30.287 --> 00:31:32.606
But causing trouble was
the last thing we wanted.

288
00:31:32.806 --> 00:31:35.537
Well. good for you.
the Axe gang is serious.

289
00:31:35.731 --> 00:31:37.085
We'll never hear
the end of this.

290
00:31:37.110 --> 00:31:38.692
Why don't you clowns just get lost?

291
00:31:39.562 --> 00:31:41.960
Why is it your wife
is always so nasty?

292
00:31:44.101 --> 00:31:45.783
Like a little massage?

293
00:31:48.277 --> 00:31:49.382
Masters.

294
00:31:56.250 --> 00:31:58.570
We have nothing
precious to offer

295
00:31:58.949 --> 00:32:00.864
but our gratitude is infinite.

296
00:32:02.497 --> 00:32:04.126
Thank you for saving us!

297
00:32:12.692 --> 00:32:15.312
Stop sniveling.
This isn't a funeral!

298
00:32:15.734 --> 00:32:19.074
-How can you be so cold-hearted.
-What's that? Keep your mouth shut.

299
00:32:19.203 --> 00:32:21.430
You may be good at
kung-fu. but you're still a fairy.

300
00:32:25.118 --> 00:32:27.117
Is it a crime to know kung-fu?

301
00:32:27.142 --> 00:32:30.448
Oh. she's gonna drown in her own
tears. once a pansy. always a pansy.

302
00:32:30.827 --> 00:32:32.201
And what's with
the red underwear?

303
00:32:32.226 --> 00:32:34.127
Is that so they can find
your rear end at night?

304
00:32:34.335 --> 00:32:35.981
You'd be better off in diapers.

305
00:32:37.601 --> 00:32:39.648
What's wrong with red underwear?

306
00:32:39.817 --> 00:32:43.071
When there was trouble. you simply
took off. while these guys saved our butts.

307
00:32:43.096 --> 00:32:44.736
And now you're trying
to chase them away.

308
00:32:44.761 --> 00:32:47.316
I'm grateful. and you should
try to be more appreciative.

309
00:32:47.341 --> 00:32:48.129
Of what?

310
00:32:48.153 --> 00:32:52.259
Every single one of you owes
me back-rent... $150. $200. $180.

311
00:32:52.342 --> 00:32:54.835
You! You owe me $95.
now pay up or pack up!

312
00:32:55.037 --> 00:32:57.351
Don't worry. guys.
I'll pay the bill.

313
00:32:57.434 --> 00:32:59.387
With what. tooth fairy?

314
00:32:59.684 --> 00:33:02.462
What's it to you where I
get my money. you fatso?

315
00:33:02.487 --> 00:33:05.080
-You little bitch!
-Look who's talking?

316
00:33:05.556 --> 00:33:08.415
Calm down. Landlady. Quit
acting like you own everybody.

317
00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:10.439
You keep out of this.
this is all your fault.

318
00:33:10.545 --> 00:33:12.365
You think you're
some kind of tyrant.

319
00:33:12.453 --> 00:33:15.370
Look at her. she's turned
her back. She doesn't care.

320
00:33:15.395 --> 00:33:17.005
How could you do that?

321
00:33:17.030 --> 00:33:19.928
Shut your mouth!

322
00:33:32.120 --> 00:33:35.607
Anyone who thinks they can out
yell me. had better think again.

323
00:33:38.181 --> 00:33:40.873
The fat cow makes a lot of
noise. I'm going to kill her.

324
00:33:42.331 --> 00:33:43.468
Watch this!

325
00:33:47.044 --> 00:33:47.860
Huh?

326
00:33:47.884 --> 00:33:48.918
You. you. you.

327
00:33:48.943 --> 00:33:50.431
You! Yeah you!

328
00:33:50.456 --> 00:33:52.364
You want to make
an issue of how I...

329
00:33:58.369 --> 00:33:59.851
What happened?

330
00:34:00.681 --> 00:34:01.681
Can you do better?

331
00:34:02.121 --> 00:34:03.363
Go on. try.

332
00:34:03.388 --> 00:34:05.356
-To throw it?
-Of course!

333
00:34:11.423 --> 00:34:13.240
Sorry! Are you okay?

334
00:34:14.233 --> 00:34:16.387
I think you should try
going a little bit closer.

335
00:34:16.411 --> 00:34:17.474
And take better aim!

336
00:34:17.651 --> 00:34:18.661
I got it!

337
00:34:30.952 --> 00:34:32.378
Who's throwing handles?

338
00:34:35.323 --> 00:34:37.726
Who did this to you?
It's missing a handle.

339
00:34:38.343 --> 00:34:40.636
I know. but that doesn't
make it feel any better.

340
00:34:40.996 --> 00:34:43.464
We should check for finger
prints. let's have a look...

341
00:34:47.684 --> 00:34:49.329
What are you trying to say?

342
00:34:49.465 --> 00:34:53.495
I forgot that I have something
important to take care off. see you later!

343
00:34:56.592 --> 00:34:58.025
Oh-no. She saw me.

344
00:34:59.963 --> 00:35:01.104
Don't make a move!

345
00:35:10.074 --> 00:35:12.014
Don't panic! Snakes
are controllable.

346
00:35:12.188 --> 00:35:14.025
one little whistle
and they will freeze.

347
00:35:14.523 --> 00:35:15.795
Please. spare me that.

348
00:35:19.459 --> 00:35:20.926
Ah. what the hell!

349
00:35:27.581 --> 00:35:29.774
Uh. you again.
you pair of idiots!

350
00:35:30.348 --> 00:35:31.921
Go home! Get back to business!

351
00:35:31.967 --> 00:35:33.575
What are you standing
around here for?

352
00:35:35.329 --> 00:35:37.089
-Let's split up!
-Split what?

353
00:35:38.881 --> 00:35:39.897
Yes!

354
00:37:53.089 --> 00:37:54.209
What are you doing here?

355
00:37:54.359 --> 00:37:56.263
Waiting for you.
Aren't you hurt?

356
00:37:56.781 --> 00:37:57.816
I'm fine!

357
00:38:00.311 --> 00:38:02.691
Where are the wounds?
Did you see a doctor?

358
00:38:03.220 --> 00:38:04.298
No. why?

359
00:38:04.943 --> 00:38:07.430
-But where have you been?
-I don't really know.

360
00:38:07.455 --> 00:38:08.411
Huh?

361
00:38:08.435 --> 00:38:09.843
Maybe it's better that way.

362
00:38:10.037 --> 00:38:12.121
Memories can
be terribly painful.

363
00:38:12.145 --> 00:38:14.855
Being able to forget
is a great blessing!

364
00:38:15.235 --> 00:38:17.451
That's quite deep. You
seemed to have learned a lot.

365
00:38:19.306 --> 00:38:21.797
All the sorrows
I've had to endure...

366
00:38:29.343 --> 00:38:32.729
I've filled a river. and now all
thoughts are sacred and pure.

367
00:38:35.357 --> 00:38:36.950
Hey. get out of the way!

368
00:38:37.065 --> 00:38:38.201
Yeah. move!

369
00:38:38.448 --> 00:38:40.109
Or I will kick your ass!

370
00:38:42.281 --> 00:38:45.255
They look like grave diggers taking
one of their customers for a walk.

371
00:38:46.515 --> 00:38:47.653
What idiots!

372
00:38:49.834 --> 00:38:52.141
I don't want to be blamed
for making you leave.

373
00:38:52.620 --> 00:38:54.370
So we will let Buddha decide

374
00:38:54.395 --> 00:38:56.562
with your ancestors
spirits as witness...

375
00:38:56.675 --> 00:38:58.662
It's all in the divining rods.

376
00:38:58.957 --> 00:39:02.001
Good stick you stay.
Bad stick you go.

377
00:39:05.758 --> 00:39:07.749
HORRIFICALLY BAD FATE

378
00:39:19.873 --> 00:39:20.926
Have some.

379
00:39:28.898 --> 00:39:32.052
We are very glad that you have come.
We need some professional advice.

380
00:39:32.125 --> 00:39:33.638
We know what your problems are.

381
00:39:33.783 --> 00:39:35.698
One is from the Hung school.

382
00:39:35.857 --> 00:39:37.577
They call him the Iron Fist.

383
00:39:37.690 --> 00:39:40.349
Those people on pig-sty
alley are really good.

384
00:39:40.399 --> 00:39:43.773
The other two are specialists of
the Twelve Kicks and Hexagon Staff.

385
00:39:43.845 --> 00:39:46.181
But their warrior
days are long over.

386
00:39:46.370 --> 00:39:49.495
Yet. kung-fu masters of their
level never cease to be a threat.

387
00:39:49.974 --> 00:39:51.170
Which makes this job.

388
00:39:51.411 --> 00:39:54.691
that you have asked us to perform
for you. a great challenge for us.

389
00:39:56.077 --> 00:39:57.671
What more can we ask?

390
00:39:57.978 --> 00:39:59.010
I told you.

391
00:39:59.035 --> 00:40:00.212
these guys are number one.

392
00:40:00.238 --> 00:40:02.100
Expensive. but totally reliable.

393
00:40:02.125 --> 00:40:03.565
They are worth every
penny they charge.

394
00:40:03.589 --> 00:40:04.346
No!

395
00:40:04.370 --> 00:40:05.869
The beast is number one.

396
00:40:05.949 --> 00:40:09.489
The evil spirit of the fire cloud
is the world's greatest killer.

397
00:40:10.056 --> 00:40:14.356
He was so dedicated to practicing
kung fu that he lost his mind.

398
00:40:14.688 --> 00:40:17.987
I have heard that he is held in
an asylum for the criminally insane.

399
00:40:18.412 --> 00:40:21.272
Which makes you the top
killers in circulation. right?

400
00:40:22.056 --> 00:40:26.425
In actuality. we are nothing more
than a pair of street musicians.

401
00:40:26.748 --> 00:40:28.757
Those tunes will
take hold of your soul.

402
00:40:28.991 --> 00:40:31.515
and then slowly
break your heart.

403
00:40:31.719 --> 00:40:32.719
Great.

404
00:40:32.914 --> 00:40:34.343
Oh. that's like poetry.

405
00:40:34.501 --> 00:40:35.761
Don't you agree?

406
00:40:44.610 --> 00:40:46.056
My friends. it is time to part.

407
00:40:46.123 --> 00:40:47.730
I hope we will meet
again someday.

408
00:40:49.473 --> 00:40:51.252
I wish I had known
we were colleagues.

409
00:40:51.613 --> 00:40:53.046
I could have done
with some company.

410
00:40:53.703 --> 00:40:56.648
Before we go our separate
ways. why don't we spar a little.

411
00:40:57.183 --> 00:41:00.239
No. thank you. I still have
lots of packing to take care of.

412
00:41:01.020 --> 00:41:03.033
-Yeah. we all do.
-Right.

413
00:41:41.412 --> 00:41:42.939
Twelve Kicks of the Tam School!

414
00:41:42.964 --> 00:41:44.582
Superb attack and defense!

415
00:41:44.607 --> 00:41:47.815
The Fist of Iron. strong and subtle
at once. A great Fist technique.

416
00:41:47.840 --> 00:41:51.004
The Woolang Staff. a many
sided technique of mystical powers!

417
00:41:51.475 --> 00:41:53.041
Until we shall meet again!

418
00:42:03.647 --> 00:42:04.647
Lipstick again!

419
00:42:24.690 --> 00:42:27.041
Stay here. or I will
break you in half.

420
00:43:50.975 --> 00:43:52.868
Sorry. but I am just closing up.

421
00:43:53.388 --> 00:43:55.069
You can make a suit in no time.

422
00:43:55.166 --> 00:43:56.656
But I am moving away.

423
00:43:57.154 --> 00:43:58.627
This is good material!

424
00:43:59.264 --> 00:44:01.307
A-hah. I see you know your cloth.

425
00:44:02.940 --> 00:44:04.793
This is very high quality.

426
00:44:04.857 --> 00:44:06.086
How high?

427
00:44:06.967 --> 00:44:08.600
How high is the sky?

428
00:45:18.673 --> 00:45:20.903
We'll show them what it
means to insult the Axe Gang!

429
00:45:20.968 --> 00:45:23.659
We will kill them and turn
this place into a whore house.

430
00:45:24.412 --> 00:45:26.000
You are blocking my view!

431
00:46:16.311 --> 00:46:17.357
What's going on?

432
00:46:17.675 --> 00:46:18.803
Ahh. forget it.

433
00:46:28.302 --> 00:46:29.338
Bullseye!

434
00:46:29.531 --> 00:46:31.071
Do not block my view.

435
00:46:36.921 --> 00:46:39.836
Damn it! I told those nit-wits
to leave. but they are still here.

436
00:46:39.863 --> 00:46:41.081
-Really?
-They are.

437
00:47:05.450 --> 00:47:07.325
What the hell is all
that racket down there?

438
00:47:07.350 --> 00:47:09.256
I got enough
problems without you...

439
00:47:09.422 --> 00:47:11.395
I'm sorry. don't pay
any attention to her!

440
00:48:52.326 --> 00:48:54.340
It's 4 o'clock. I want
to get some sleep.

441
00:48:54.364 --> 00:48:55.420
Get out of here.

442
00:48:55.840 --> 00:48:57.207
Shut up. you hag!

443
00:48:57.400 --> 00:48:58.640
It's time to die!

444
00:48:59.243 --> 00:49:00.610
Die. my ass.

445
00:49:00.635 --> 00:49:02.661
Don't listen to her!

446
00:49:05.224 --> 00:49:06.921
You are still blocking the view!

447
00:49:08.195 --> 00:49:09.244
Hang in there.

448
00:49:18.738 --> 00:49:20.865
Be quiet!

449
00:49:25.946 --> 00:49:27.931
Give us a break!
Get out of here!

450
00:49:28.718 --> 00:49:30.553
Are you trying to kill us all?

451
00:49:41.312 --> 00:49:42.319
The view!

452
00:49:45.314 --> 00:49:46.892
I sense another master.

453
00:52:14.033 --> 00:52:16.320
It was the Roar.
The Lion's Roar!

454
00:52:16.783 --> 00:52:18.013
I thought it was a myth.

455
00:52:19.406 --> 00:52:21.441
Why didn't you tell
me that it really exists?

456
00:52:22.544 --> 00:52:24.177
That is the last
we will see of them.

457
00:52:25.091 --> 00:52:26.091
Right?

458
00:52:26.135 --> 00:52:27.231
-Hmm.

459
00:52:29.085 --> 00:52:29.973
This is bad. boss.

460
00:52:29.997 --> 00:52:31.384
Get the car started. quick!

461
00:52:32.054 --> 00:52:33.152
I told you to get...

462
00:52:40.531 --> 00:52:41.568
What now?

463
00:52:41.685 --> 00:52:42.728
Keep it down!

464
00:52:42.775 --> 00:52:43.882
Don't you have any manners?

465
00:52:43.948 --> 00:52:45.382
These a working
class neighborhood.

466
00:52:45.407 --> 00:52:46.768
People have to be at work at 8.

467
00:52:46.933 --> 00:52:48.760
So get the hell out of my sight!

468
00:52:49.043 --> 00:52:50.105
Right now!

469
00:52:52.877 --> 00:52:54.402
What a bunch of hoodlums!

470
00:54:20.576 --> 00:54:23.735
It is no use. I cannot
hold out much longer.

471
00:54:26.385 --> 00:54:29.851
But having met true
masters like you...

472
00:54:30.429 --> 00:54:32.204
I can now die in peace.

473
00:54:32.416 --> 00:54:34.296
Don't say things
like that. Donut.

474
00:54:34.669 --> 00:54:37.861
We are just an ordinary couple.
that is trying to live in peace.

475
00:54:38.143 --> 00:54:39.477
Fighting is futile.

476
00:54:39.736 --> 00:54:41.144
Where as a normal life.

477
00:54:41.303 --> 00:54:43.193
is all that one
should aspire to.

478
00:54:43.601 --> 00:54:45.420
But you are so
good at martial arts.

479
00:54:45.500 --> 00:54:47.019
If only you'd helped us earlier.

480
00:54:47.044 --> 00:54:48.813
all this would never
have happened..

481
00:54:50.531 --> 00:54:53.966
Everybody has his good reasons.

482
00:54:55.073 --> 00:54:57.409
Several years ago. my
poor husband and I...

483
00:54:57.563 --> 00:55:00.309
we saw our only son
beaten to death in a fight.

484
00:55:02.989 --> 00:55:04.932
Revenge can be devastating.

485
00:55:05.945 --> 00:55:07.887
Do you understand
what I am saying?

486
00:55:08.362 --> 00:55:11.560
There is only one solution to the matter.
you must teach us all that you know.

487
00:55:11.632 --> 00:55:14.443
Help us become kung-fu
fighters and we will avenge them!

488
00:55:14.576 --> 00:55:18.831
But it takes years to reach the
top. Being a fighter is not easy.

489
00:55:19.066 --> 00:55:21.627
Either you are born with
the calling. or you are not.

490
00:55:21.697 --> 00:55:24.972
And the chances of that
are about one in a million.

491
00:55:32.917 --> 00:55:35.418
It is obvious. I am
the chosen one.

492
00:55:38.762 --> 00:55:40.958
No. doesn't got what it takes.

493
00:55:42.019 --> 00:55:43.019
Listen!

494
00:55:43.110 --> 00:55:45.351
We swore that we would never fight again.

495
00:55:45.394 --> 00:55:47.463
That we would rest our skills forever.

496
00:55:47.488 --> 00:55:49.762
Tonight we broke
that solemn promise.

497
00:55:49.956 --> 00:55:51.250
For your own good.

498
00:55:51.504 --> 00:55:53.344
why don't you all
just all go away.

499
00:55:57.938 --> 00:55:59.497
With great power.

500
00:56:00.396 --> 00:56:01.404
comes

501
00:56:01.804 --> 00:56:03.903
great responsibility.

502
00:56:04.411 --> 00:56:05.436
Donut.

503
00:56:05.729 --> 00:56:07.209
you are badly hurt.

504
00:56:07.267 --> 00:56:08.742
You must keep still.

505
00:56:08.940 --> 00:56:10.203
This could be the end

506
00:56:10.228 --> 00:56:11.297
of a beautiful

507
00:56:11.799 --> 00:56:12.805
friendship!

508
00:56:12.865 --> 00:56:13.884
No. Donut.

509
00:56:13.909 --> 00:56:15.437
Tomorrow is another day.

510
00:56:17.786 --> 00:56:18.877
Donut!

511
00:56:32.088 --> 00:56:34.080
Hi there. four-eyes!

512
00:56:35.260 --> 00:56:37.907
I. ah... note that your
tolerance for the

513
00:56:38.233 --> 00:56:39.981
sight-impaired
is rather limited.

514
00:56:40.144 --> 00:56:41.043
That's right.

515
00:56:41.067 --> 00:56:43.044
Especially when they're
wearing gold-frames.

516
00:56:47.192 --> 00:56:48.174
I'm a clerk.

517
00:56:48.198 --> 00:56:49.891
Gold frames look good on clerks.

518
00:56:49.916 --> 00:56:51.671
I like the way I look.

519
00:56:51.733 --> 00:56:53.587
So don't hassle
me. you little fool.

520
00:56:56.783 --> 00:56:57.783
Help me!

521
00:56:59.970 --> 00:57:00.797
Alley cats.

522
00:57:00.821 --> 00:57:01.731
mongrels.

523
00:57:01.755 --> 00:57:02.422
dogs.

524
00:57:02.446 --> 00:57:03.280
rats.

525
00:57:03.304 --> 00:57:04.186
wretches.

526
00:57:04.210 --> 00:57:05.210
worms!

527
00:57:08.554 --> 00:57:10.017
So much for your... so-so-so-so.

528
00:57:10.042 --> 00:57:11.096
Come down here.

529
00:57:11.143 --> 00:57:13.070
and I'll shove your
glasses down your throat.

530
00:57:13.257 --> 00:57:14.290
You hear me?

531
00:57:16.204 --> 00:57:18.153
You know damn well that
I would have done that.

532
00:57:19.646 --> 00:57:20.686
Was that a yes?

533
00:57:21.577 --> 00:57:22.601
I would have!

534
00:57:25.681 --> 00:57:27.233
You have no respect. huh?

535
00:57:27.901 --> 00:57:29.821
You're never there
when I need you.

536
00:57:31.721 --> 00:57:32.780
You sound like a wimp!

537
00:57:33.590 --> 00:57:35.515
Because of you we're
always getting beaten up.

538
00:57:35.980 --> 00:57:37.117
We have nothing to show.

539
00:57:37.157 --> 00:57:39.456
No murder. no rape. no
arson. no theft. no nothing!

540
00:57:39.481 --> 00:57:40.610
We have not gotten anywhere.

541
00:57:40.635 --> 00:57:43.235
I know that. because you
can't get your fat ass in gear.

542
00:57:43.535 --> 00:57:45.795
What have I done to
deserve you as a partner?

543
00:57:48.513 --> 00:57:49.526
Lets go!

544
00:57:58.704 --> 00:58:00.331
This is a stickup!
Where's the money?

545
00:58:05.144 --> 00:58:06.214
Where's the money?

546
00:58:06.239 --> 00:58:07.246
Give it to me.

547
00:58:09.003 --> 00:58:10.149
Don't look at me like that.

548
00:58:10.174 --> 00:58:11.182
I mean it!

549
00:58:15.971 --> 00:58:17.417
I have killed people for less!

550
00:58:17.442 --> 00:58:18.457
Now get the money.

551
00:58:18.771 --> 00:58:19.817
Go on!

552
00:58:38.602 --> 00:58:39.882
-It's in here.
-Huh?

553
00:59:15.810 --> 00:59:17.473
Let her go!

554
00:59:30.831 --> 00:59:33.813
The total idiot. and a deaf mute!

555
00:59:33.838 --> 00:59:35.625
What a bunch of losers.

556
01:00:19.488 --> 01:00:21.779
Leave me alone!
You're just dead weight!

557
01:00:23.120 --> 01:00:24.500
Here. take this.

558
01:00:24.525 --> 01:00:25.811
Go home and raise pigs.

559
01:00:26.744 --> 01:00:28.292
That is where you belong.

560
01:00:32.643 --> 01:00:34.331
Go on. before I kill you!

561
01:01:23.937 --> 01:01:25.029
Hey. kid!

562
01:01:25.632 --> 01:01:27.076
Hey. what's your name?

563
01:01:35.909 --> 01:01:37.969
Here you go. buy
yourself some new clothes.

564
01:01:37.993 --> 01:01:39.571
You now a member
of The Axe gang.

565
01:01:39.596 --> 01:01:40.543
Are you serious?

566
01:01:40.567 --> 01:01:43.218
Yes. and there's someone
back here waiting for you.

567
01:01:50.349 --> 01:01:51.427
Brother Sum.

568
01:01:51.452 --> 01:01:53.041
When I first saw you.

569
01:01:53.268 --> 01:01:55.946
I knew you'd be a courageous
man of many talents.

570
01:01:56.483 --> 01:01:57.483
Uh-huh.

571
01:01:57.650 --> 01:01:59.448
Looking for an opportunity.

572
01:02:00.253 --> 01:02:01.279
Right!

573
01:02:01.455 --> 01:02:03.116
I have an assignment for you.

574
01:02:03.290 --> 01:02:04.848
For you I would eat fire.

575
01:02:18.605 --> 01:02:19.787
Come on. Move.

576
01:02:22.999 --> 01:02:25.827
"Research for
abnormal development."

577
01:02:25.852 --> 01:02:27.873
-What's that?
-A nut-house for crazy people.

578
01:02:28.340 --> 01:02:29.432
Down!

579
01:02:29.992 --> 01:02:31.905
-Reporting. sir!
-Good work.

580
01:02:34.425 --> 01:02:35.654
What is the army doing there?

581
01:02:35.786 --> 01:02:37.514
Those are not soldiers.
They're Boy Scouts.

582
01:02:37.729 --> 01:02:38.729
With tanks?

583
01:02:39.242 --> 01:02:40.865
Forget it. they are just models.

584
01:02:40.998 --> 01:02:44.718
Now. when those scouts change the
guards. five minutes is all you will have.

585
01:02:44.837 --> 01:02:48.056
You must follow these arrows
to the last cell. When you find it

586
01:02:48.131 --> 01:02:51.008
force the door. and
get the man in there out.

587
01:02:51.134 --> 01:02:53.368
Here's your tool kit.
Five minutes. Now go!

588
01:02:59.519 --> 01:03:00.939
And... what about you?

589
01:03:00.964 --> 01:03:02.955
We will be your
lookouts. of course.

590
01:03:14.115 --> 01:03:16.144
You have 5 minutes.
Get on with it.

591
01:05:30.855 --> 01:05:32.115
The world's finest killer.

592
01:05:32.140 --> 01:05:35.301
the Beast himself. is clearly
dressed to suit his reputation.

593
01:05:36.328 --> 01:05:38.837
That is only a
label. Do not worry.

594
01:05:38.977 --> 01:05:41.803
We want two people killed and
you're the one who's going to do it.

595
01:05:41.827 --> 01:05:42.903
Now. what do you charge?

596
01:05:42.928 --> 01:05:44.452
What do I charge?

597
01:05:46.852 --> 01:05:48.938
I killed so many over the years.

598
01:05:49.078 --> 01:05:52.038
so many. just trying to
find a worthy adversary.

599
01:05:52.192 --> 01:05:53.960
That's why I stay in my cell.

600
01:05:53.985 --> 01:05:56.059
because there was
no one out there.

601
01:05:56.641 --> 01:05:59.539
I would have escaped long
ago if I had found someone.

602
01:05:59.928 --> 01:06:02.104
If you find me such an opponent.

603
01:06:02.695 --> 01:06:03.811
then. young friend.

604
01:06:04.057 --> 01:06:06.441
I will make you an
offer you cannot refuse.

605
01:06:06.466 --> 01:06:08.015
I will do it for free.

606
01:06:09.971 --> 01:06:11.185
Do you have someone?

607
01:06:11.400 --> 01:06:14.126
Yes! We have just what you
are looking for. the very best.

608
01:06:14.208 --> 01:06:16.694
This is gonna be the
fight of the century!

609
01:06:16.806 --> 01:06:19.137
Would you mind demonstrating
some of your technique.

610
01:06:19.308 --> 01:06:20.693
Not that we don't trust you.

611
01:06:20.753 --> 01:06:22.440
We just want to see
what we are buying.

612
01:06:22.885 --> 01:06:24.638
You fools are not worth it.

613
01:06:24.662 --> 01:06:26.811
I am just wasting my time here.

614
01:06:30.087 --> 01:06:31.250
Yes. boss.

615
01:06:31.517 --> 01:06:32.799
He looks like refuse.

616
01:06:34.092 --> 01:06:36.531
I agree. those sandals
look totally worn out.

617
01:06:36.611 --> 01:06:39.138
But a change of clothes would
make him look quite respectable.

618
01:06:39.339 --> 01:06:41.172
Are you sure you
brought the right one?

619
01:06:41.197 --> 01:06:42.370
Oh. yes. boss. I am certain.

620
01:06:42.394 --> 01:06:44.245
I swear I followed
your order to the letter.

621
01:06:46.796 --> 01:06:49.052
Mr Beast. please show us
a sample of your technique.

622
01:06:49.076 --> 01:06:50.132
My career is on the line.

623
01:06:50.309 --> 01:06:51.656
What do I care?

624
01:06:52.631 --> 01:06:54.388
Okay. old man. You see this?

625
01:06:55.329 --> 01:06:57.555
Have you ever gone
up against a fist this big?

626
01:06:57.819 --> 01:06:59.334
I am almost afraid to use it.

627
01:06:59.388 --> 01:07:00.993
Do you realize the
danger you're in?

628
01:07:01.018 --> 01:07:02.701
Really? Try me. then.

629
01:07:06.773 --> 01:07:07.782
See what I mean.

630
01:07:07.806 --> 01:07:08.940
Is he conscious?

631
01:07:14.837 --> 01:07:17.512
Aha. and you say you can fight?

632
01:07:18.700 --> 01:07:19.700
Harder!

633
01:07:21.122 --> 01:07:22.122
Harder!

634
01:07:24.860 --> 01:07:26.191
Much harder!

635
01:07:28.673 --> 01:07:30.382
If that is all you
have to offer.

636
01:07:30.407 --> 01:07:32.345
how come you call
yourself a gangster?

637
01:07:37.013 --> 01:07:38.451
Do they make this for men?

638
01:08:05.185 --> 01:08:09.718
In the world of kung-fu.
speed determines the winner.

639
01:08:13.881 --> 01:08:16.783
That leaves no doubt about
who our honored guest is.

640
01:08:17.206 --> 01:08:18.515
Your skill is unique.

641
01:08:18.540 --> 01:08:20.468
The Axe Gang offers its respect.

642
01:09:02.294 --> 01:09:05.255
The three true
masters of kung-fu.

643
01:09:06.713 --> 01:09:10.613
Only the world's top killer
exudes an aura like that.

644
01:09:11.317 --> 01:09:13.194
It crowds the air.

645
01:09:13.323 --> 01:09:15.291
And what is that
other aura telling me?

646
01:09:15.410 --> 01:09:18.371
Am I looking at the legendary
tragic couple? The great...

647
01:09:18.418 --> 01:09:19.608
Yuen Wah.

648
01:09:19.728 --> 01:09:20.954
And the dragons daughter.

649
01:09:21.386 --> 01:09:23.139
It is a great honor to be here.

650
01:09:23.193 --> 01:09:24.766
We have come to

651
01:09:25.252 --> 01:09:27.028
eliminate The Axe Gang

652
01:09:27.410 --> 01:09:29.020
and only the Axe Gang.

653
01:09:31.835 --> 01:09:34.122
You should have killed me
while you had the chance.

654
01:09:34.264 --> 01:09:35.633
But it is too late.

655
01:09:36.157 --> 01:09:38.913
Now that you are here.
you are doomed to die.

656
01:09:39.063 --> 01:09:40.819
You are living on borrowed time.

657
01:09:40.844 --> 01:09:42.219
Your fate is sealed.

658
01:09:42.415 --> 01:09:45.161
We brought you a
gift you cannot refuse!

659
01:09:46.146 --> 01:09:48.211
What is this. a funeral bell?

660
01:09:48.724 --> 01:09:49.458
Ha!

661
01:09:49.482 --> 01:09:52.533
With the beast on our side. we
shall see for whom the bell tolls.

662
01:09:54.020 --> 01:09:55.475
Are you here on their behalf?

663
01:09:55.508 --> 01:09:56.037
Huh?

664
01:09:56.061 --> 01:09:57.671
Don't misunderstand me.

665
01:09:57.885 --> 01:10:01.097
The only thing I'm here
for is to kill the two of you.

666
01:10:01.348 --> 01:10:04.593
Or for you to kill me. if
you have what it takes.

667
01:10:06.995 --> 01:10:08.597
What is your opinion. dear?

668
01:10:08.923 --> 01:10:10.962
In this world good cannot exist

669
01:10:11.529 --> 01:10:13.026
along side with evil.

670
01:10:13.209 --> 01:10:14.816
Such is destiny.

671
01:10:15.171 --> 01:10:16.812
Then that is the decision.

672
01:10:17.995 --> 01:10:19.045
Shall we?

673
01:10:19.315 --> 01:10:20.347
Okay.

674
01:10:21.970 --> 01:10:22.994
Let's dance!

675
01:10:43.094 --> 01:10:45.389
That's okay for starters.
Now let's try again.

676
01:10:54.634 --> 01:10:57.660
That was much better. but
you are still lacking precision.

677
01:12:17.068 --> 01:12:19.109
The Lion's Roar!

678
01:15:00.306 --> 01:15:01.346
Wait!

679
01:15:02.824 --> 01:15:05.064
Nobody told me the Lion's Roar

680
01:15:05.264 --> 01:15:07.197
could be done
through a loud speaker!

681
01:15:07.630 --> 01:15:09.961
I concede my defeat.

682
01:15:39.465 --> 01:15:40.631
Looks like he's not up to it.

683
01:15:40.655 --> 01:15:42.797
This is our big chance. Get
them while they are down.

684
01:15:42.868 --> 01:15:43.868
You do it!

685
01:15:44.575 --> 01:15:47.212
-I'm gonna be sick. I need a doctor.
-Go to hell!

686
01:15:51.431 --> 01:15:52.331
You!

687
01:15:52.355 --> 01:15:53.392
Come here.

688
01:15:54.381 --> 01:15:55.718
-Hit him!
-Okay.

689
01:16:00.988 --> 01:16:02.554
-On the head!
-Yes. sir!

690
01:16:03.058 --> 01:16:04.787
-Hit him on the head!
-Okay.

691
01:16:05.033 --> 01:16:06.308
-Now's your chance.
-Right!

692
01:16:06.827 --> 01:16:08.048
-Go on!
-I will!

693
01:16:08.260 --> 01:16:09.720
-Smash him on the head!
-I will!

694
01:16:09.745 --> 01:16:11.287
-On the head!
-I will!

695
01:16:11.334 --> 01:16:12.661
Beat him to a pulp!

696
01:16:15.444 --> 01:16:16.444
What was that?

697
01:16:16.706 --> 01:16:19.484
Do you want me to beat him to a
pulp. or just smash him on the head?

698
01:16:19.829 --> 01:16:21.764
You are totally confusing me!

699
01:16:50.276 --> 01:16:52.241
Wow. A pretty big
fist you have there.

700
01:16:52.455 --> 01:16:53.489
Careful with that.

701
01:17:25.849 --> 01:17:27.315
Why did you hit me?

702
01:17:55.957 --> 01:17:57.046
Where are they?!

703
01:17:57.742 --> 01:17:59.013
They are gone!

704
01:17:59.473 --> 01:18:01.954
You're completely useless!
You let them get away!

705
01:18:07.992 --> 01:18:10.268
I cannot be defeated.

706
01:18:10.292 --> 01:18:12.143
Not in this world.

707
01:18:25.629 --> 01:18:27.297
Why did he try to save us?

708
01:18:27.985 --> 01:18:31.080
These young people often make
mistakes when they are starting out.

709
01:18:31.728 --> 01:18:32.962
We must forgive them.

710
01:18:32.986 --> 01:18:34.695
if they make good in the end.

711
01:18:34.953 --> 01:18:35.903
Oh!

712
01:18:35.927 --> 01:18:36.993
Just look.

713
01:18:37.160 --> 01:18:38.648
Beaten to a pulp.

714
01:18:38.673 --> 01:18:39.860
The poor boy.

715
01:18:42.521 --> 01:18:44.254
Do you have a last request?

716
01:18:44.358 --> 01:18:45.748
Just tell us.

717
01:19:04.960 --> 01:19:05.922
Wait.

718
01:19:05.946 --> 01:19:07.553
Wait... what are you writing?

719
01:19:08.229 --> 01:19:09.975
I do not know this character.

720
01:19:10.143 --> 01:19:11.662
I cannot understand.

721
01:19:12.029 --> 01:19:13.042
Wait.

722
01:19:13.382 --> 01:19:14.440
Wait.

723
01:20:09.089 --> 01:20:10.143
No one here.

724
01:20:15.238 --> 01:20:17.867
CHINESE MEDICINE

725
01:20:31.409 --> 01:20:34.559
It is truly a miracle he
has survived this long.

726
01:20:34.945 --> 01:20:36.633
Your herbs are
playing their part.

727
01:20:37.603 --> 01:20:39.286
The herbs will help him along.

728
01:20:39.586 --> 01:20:41.806
But the key lies
within his own body.

729
01:20:42.742 --> 01:20:45.648
All his bones are
broken. his tendons torn.

730
01:20:45.799 --> 01:20:48.181
It is amazing he is
recovering so quickly.

731
01:20:48.671 --> 01:20:52.145
Under normal circumstances
this would be impossible. unless...

732
01:20:52.193 --> 01:20:53.751
Unless of course...

733
01:21:31.235 --> 01:21:32.337
Smell that?

734
01:22:06.729 --> 01:22:08.721
You must not smoke
while you are injured.

735
01:22:10.845 --> 01:22:12.334
Let me deal with this.

736
01:22:26.577 --> 01:22:28.083
This makes no sense.

737
01:22:39.738 --> 01:22:41.493
Who would ever have thought

738
01:22:41.666 --> 01:22:44.746
that the boy's chi-flow
would be released by the

739
01:22:44.793 --> 01:22:46.246
Beast's thrashing?

740
01:22:46.780 --> 01:22:47.780
Right.

741
01:22:47.819 --> 01:22:49.853
Still. we should
have noticed earlier.

742
01:22:50.876 --> 01:22:54.140
That he may be the greatest
kung-fu genius to ever come along.

743
01:23:04.654 --> 01:23:06.528
I wonder what
he'll be up to next?

744
01:23:07.108 --> 01:23:09.443
So. you're still
alive. you traitor.

745
01:23:09.484 --> 01:23:11.564
Axes. forward!

746
01:24:06.949 --> 01:24:08.416
The toe crusher.

747
01:24:08.658 --> 01:24:11.182
That went out of style
when I left kindergarten.

748
01:24:39.158 --> 01:24:42.754
Our son would have been
just about his age now.

749
01:24:43.195 --> 01:24:45.228
If he is willing to
make the effort

750
01:24:45.416 --> 01:24:48.164
he could surely become
a doctor or a lawyer.

751
01:24:48.421 --> 01:24:50.555
More likely a great
kung-fu fighter.

752
01:25:54.108 --> 01:25:55.101
Not bad.

753
01:25:55.125 --> 01:25:56.168
Now what?

754
01:26:37.563 --> 01:26:38.759
Child's play.

755
01:26:38.942 --> 01:26:40.346
I can stop bullets.

756
01:27:51.579 --> 01:27:52.409
Huh?

757
01:27:52.433 --> 01:27:54.809
Isn't that the Toad
technique of the Kwan Lun?

758
01:27:55.068 --> 01:27:56.370
I am afraid so.

759
01:29:51.777 --> 01:29:55.579
Do you remember the Buddhist technique
of the Palm descending from heaven?

760
01:29:55.670 --> 01:29:58.834
The long lost art we all
thought was forever gone.

761
01:30:43.230 --> 01:30:45.455
I surrender!

762
01:31:46.194 --> 01:31:48.023
What's the name
of your technique?

763
01:31:49.578 --> 01:31:50.703
Do you want to learn?

764
01:31:50.780 --> 01:31:51.904
I will teach you.

765
01:32:03.919 --> 01:32:05.295
Master!

766
01:33:18.528 --> 01:33:22.015
Would you tell your son not to
smear his snot all over the glass.

767
01:33:22.521 --> 01:33:24.827
You two! Don't put
your pants down in here!

768
01:33:25.583 --> 01:33:28.003
Hey. if you lick it
you have to buy it. kid.

769
01:34:34.320 --> 01:34:38.917
Sonny. you have the structure
of the chi-flow of a kung-fu genius.

770
01:34:39.006 --> 01:34:41.504
